nii ningwenda, Ngai umenyage 
ningenaga muno niwe
tondu niunjikaga wega
na ukanyenda hingo ciothe

irio ciakwa iria ndiaga
mai maria nyuaga
ona nguo cia kwihumba
ciothe nowe uheaga.

muoyo naguo nowe waheire
niwe ugiragia ngue
ungithengia hinya waku
ndingiikara gathaa kamwe

we muthenya ona utuku
niumenyagirira wega
maitho maku no mambaaraga
kuri nduma kana utheri

ndingihota gukugathira 
wega waku mwathwni
no nindakuhoya utumage
ngwend muno na nguiguage
